"A.P.238/4/9/12:00": "...There's a change in the atmosphere. Looks like the end is ahead."
"Before we go to the last area, can I ask you something?"
"There were any number of other people you could have partnered with, right?"
"...You don't need to say anything, I can tell by the look on your face. Honestly, I don't want or need your concern..."
"Sooner or later, you'll slip up and draw the short straw at the worst possible time."
"But, thanks. I've had a lot of fun thanks to you."
"I wasn't planning to take part in this. And on top of that, teaming up with someone..."
"As far as I was concerned, it all had nothing to do with me."
"...Well, let's go. We've come this far, so we should definitely see the end."
